This paper is about click through rate (CTR) prediction, which is a common problem in online advertising and feed ranking. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
